{"tid":1088820,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【布差拉提】壯烈成仁仲屈過紫煙","createTime":"2019-04-02T10:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T15:39:09.000Z","uid":61443,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d0a79b080e4d50d9a787d06b9935f2e0758f5f","tid":1088820,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:19:13.000Z","msg":"紫煙都話要近攻發動 <br />\n壯烈成仁射程有成架火車咁撚長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然冇紫煙接近 99% 死亡 <br />\n但衰老你都冇晒力同等死冇分別<br />\n仲要掂到你可以急速老死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話就話有體温下降破解<br />\n但個感覺似超人氦氣石揾啲嘢搞到唔係無敵咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：布差拉提救全家"},{"pid":"973a986fa9a5326fd5611c0c3e821b027696e4b8","tid":1088820,"uid":197836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:21:45.000Z","msg":"紫煙根本吹大左"},{"pid":"3709bdc783e3ab13bf334f0f47609be06ab0c6fa","tid":1088820,"uid":20148,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:25:37.000Z","msg":"白色相簿克死佢"},{"pid":"67e668f612a709cd3dcfd550becb7d7a939c024d","tid":1088820,"uid":61443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"973a986fa9a5326fd5611c0c3e821b027696e4b8","tid":1088820,"uid":197836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:21:45.000Z","msg":"紫煙根本吹大左"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:25:52.000Z","msg":"點解釋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇最強替身<br />\n只有最強用家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af96c10476d4e6927a8f6e6d0adee9158e4c61d3","tid":1088820,"uid":74004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67e668f612a709cd3dcfd550becb7d7a939c024d","tid":1088820,"uid":61443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"973a986fa9a5326fd5611c0c3e821b027696e4b8","tid":1088820,"uid":197836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:21:45.000Z","msg":"紫煙根